{"type": "article", "id": 28765, "title": "条纹镜", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-28T06:53:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121008Jmfo9Yq7Hwx5rnP6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这个由条纹图案构成的镜子 New Perspective 是设计师 <a href=\"http://www.alaingilles.com/en\">Alain Gilles</a> 为意大利品牌 <a href=\"http://bonaldo.it/it\">Bonaldo</a> 设计的产品。Gilles 打破常规，将自己的创作草图印在镜面上，卡通风格的注入为普通的镜子带来了一种温暖轻松的感觉。New Perspective 一共有两种尺寸可选，较小的版本配有一个无烟煤色的橡木搁板，挂在墙上也变成了一个放置小物的理想之选。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121006FcRoZivnQbtGOMge.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.61369193\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121007nAVq9syiZv267HbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84107579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121007BI1eSztc9QK6G85W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90220049\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121007LEhvSk9IebtKx12l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}